<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, viewport-fit=cover" />
<title>FleetFlow TMS — Dispatch, compliance, and same-day pay on one screen</title>
<meta name="description" content="The dispatch hub for 3-to-50-truck carriers and brokers. Kill the spreadsheet, capture POD on the driver's phone, get paid the day you deliver." />
<style>
:root{
  --ink:#0F172A; --ink-2:#1E293B; --slate:#475569; --mute:#64748B; --line:#E2E8F0;
  --bg:#F8FAFC; --bg-2:#FFFFFF; --brand:#0F172A; --accent:#F59E0B; --good:#10B981;
}
*{box-sizing:border-box}
html,body{margin:0;padding:0;background:var(--bg);color:var(--ink);font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Inter,Arial,sans-serif;line-height:1.55;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased}
a{color:inherit}
.wrap{max-width:1120px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px}
.btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:14px 22px;border-radius:10px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;font-size:15px;transition:transform .08s ease,background .15s ease}
.btn:active{transform:translateY(1px)}
.btn-primary{background:var(--ink);color:#fff}
.btn-primary:hover{background:#1E293B}
.btn-ghost{background:transparent;color:var(--ink);border:1px solid var(--line)}
.btn-ghost:hover{background:#fff}
header.nav{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:50;background:rgba(248,250,252,.85);backdrop-filter:saturate(140%) blur(8px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}
.nav-row{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;height:64px}
.logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-0.01em}
.logo .mark{width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:7px;background:var(--ink);position:relative;display:inline-block}
.logo .mark:after{content:"";position:absolute;inset:6px;border-radius:3px;border:2px solid var(--accent);border-right:none;border-bottom:none}
.nav-links{display:flex;gap:24px;align-items:center;color:var(--slate);font-size:14px}
.nav-links a{text-decoration:none}
.nav-links a:hover{color:var(--ink)}

/* HERO */
.hero{padding:88px 0 64px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}
.eyebrow{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:6px 12px;border-radius:999px;background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--slate);font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:20px}
.eyebrow .dot{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--good);box-shadow:0 0 0 4px rgba(16,185,129,.12)}
.h1{font-size:56px;line-height:1.05;letter-spacing:-0.02em;font-weight:800;margin:0 0 18px;max-width:880px}
.h1 em{font-style:normal;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--ink),var(--accent));-webkit-background-clip:text;background-clip:text;color:transparent}
.sub{font-size:19px;color:var(--slate);max-width:680px;margin:0 0 28px}
.cta-row{display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center}
.cta-trust{margin-top:18px;color:var(--mute);font-size:13px}

/* board mockup */
.board{margin-top:48px;background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:16px;box-shadow:0 30px 80px -40px rgba(15,23,42,.25),0 2px 0 rgba(15,23,42,.02);overflow:hidden}
.board-head{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:14px 20px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);background:#fff}
.board-title{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;font-weight:600;font-size:14px;color:var(--ink-2)}
.board-controls{display:flex;gap:8px;font-size:12px;color:var(--mute)}
.board-controls span{padding:4px 10px;border-radius:6px;background:#F1F5F9;color:var(--slate)}
table.board-tbl{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:13.5px}
.board-tbl thead th{text-align:left;font-weight:600;color:var(--mute);text-transform:uppercase;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.04em;padding:10px 16px;background:#F8FAFC;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}
.board-tbl tbody td{padding:12px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid #F1F5F9;color:var(--ink-2)}
.board-tbl tbody tr:hover td{background:#F8FAFC}
.pill{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;padding:2px 9px;border-radius:999px;border:1px solid;background:#fff}
.p-avail{color:#475569;border-color:#CBD5E1;background:#F1F5F9}
.p-assigned{color:#1D4ED8;border-color:#BFDBFE;background:#EFF6FF}
.p-transit{color:#92400E;border-color:#FCD34D;background:#FEF3C7}
.p-delivered{color:#065F46;border-color:#A7F3D0;background:#ECFDF5}
.p-invoiced{color:#5B21B6;border-color:#DDD6FE;background:#F5F3FF}
.right{text-align:right}
.mono{font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;font-feature-settings:"tnum"}

/* features */
section{padding:80px 0}
.section-eyebrow{color:var(--mute);text-transform:uppercase;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.08em;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:10px}
.section-title{font-size:36px;letter-spacing:-0.015em;font-weight:800;margin:0 0 44px;max-width:760px}
.grid-3{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:20px}
.card{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:14px;padding:24px}
.card h3{margin:0 0 8px;font-size:18px;letter-spacing:-0.01em}
.card p{margin:0 0 14px;color:var(--slate);font-size:15px}
.benefit{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-size:13px;color:var(--ink-2);background:#F1F5F9;padding:6px 10px;border-radius:8px;font-weight:600}
.benefit svg{width:14px;height:14px;color:var(--good)}

/* how */
.steps{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:24px;counter-reset:s}
.step{counter-increment:s;background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:14px;padding:24px;position:relative}
.step:before{content:counter(s,decimal-leading-zero);position:absolute;top:-12px;left:20px;background:var(--ink);color:#fff;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:8px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.05em}
.step h3{margin:6px 0 8px;font-size:18px}
.step p{margin:0;color:var(--slate);font-size:14.5px}

/* pricing */
.price{background:#0F172A;color:#fff;border-radius:18px;padding:48px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.2fr 1fr;gap:40px;align-items:center}
.price h2{font-size:36px;letter-spacing:-0.015em;margin:0 0 12px}
.price p{color:#CBD5E1;margin:0 0 18px}
.price ul{margin:0;padding:0 0 0 18px;color:#CBD5E1;font-size:14.5px}
.price ul li{margin:6px 0}
.price .num{font-size:64px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1}
.price .per{color:#94A3B8;font-size:14px;margin-top:8px}
.price .founder{margin-top:18px;font-size:13px;color:#FDE68A;background:rgba(245,158,11,.1);border:1px solid rgba(245,158,11,.3);padding:10px 14px;border-radius:10px;display:inline-block}

/* faq */
details.q{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:12px;padding:18px 22px;margin-bottom:10px}
details.q[open]{border-color:#CBD5E1}
details.q summary{cursor:pointer;font-weight:600;font-size:15.5px;list-style:none;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center}
details.q summary::-webkit-details-marker{display:none}
details.q summary:after{content:"+";color:var(--mute);font-size:20px;line-height:1}
details.q[open] summary:after{content:"–"}
details.q p{margin:12px 0 0;color:var(--slate);font-size:14.5px}

/* final cta */
.final{text-align:center;background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:18px;padding:56px 24px}
.final h2{font-size:34px;letter-spacing:-0.015em;margin:0 0 12px}
.final p{color:var(--slate);max-width:560px;margin:0 auto 28px;font-size:16px}

footer{padding:36px 0;border-top:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--mute);font-size:13px}
.foot-row{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:12px}

@media (max-width:820px){
  .h1{font-size:40px}
  .grid-3,.steps{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .price{grid-template-columns:1fr;padding:32px}
  .price .num{font-size:48px}
  .board-tbl thead th:nth-child(3),.board-tbl tbody td:nth-child(3){display:none}
  .board-tbl thead th:nth-child(4),.board-tbl tbody td:nth-child(4){display:none}
  .nav-links a:not(:last-child){display:none}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header class="nav">
  <div class="wrap nav-row">
    <div class="logo"><span class="mark"></span> FleetFlow</div>
    <nav class="nav-links">
      <a href="#features">Features</a>
      <a href="#how">How it works</a>
      <a href="#pricing">Pricing</a>
      <a href="#faq">FAQ</a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="#cta" style="padding:8px 14px;font-size:14px">Book a demo</a>
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#cta" style="padding:8px 14px;font-size:14px">Start trial</a>
    </nav>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <span class="eyebrow"><span class="dot"></span> Now onboarding founding fleets — $27/truck for life</span>
    <h1 class="h1">Dispatch, compliance, and <em>same-day pay</em> — one screen.</h1>
    <p class="sub">FleetFlow is the dispatch hub for 3-to-50-truck fleets and brokers who are done running their business on Sheets, email threads, and a stack of paper BOLs.</p>
    <div class="cta-row">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#cta">Start the 30-day trial →</a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="#cta">Book a 20-min walkthrough</a>
    </div>
    <p class="cta-trust">No credit card to start · Cancel any time · Your data exports as CSV</p>

    <!-- product mockup -->
    <div class="board" aria-label="Dispatch board preview">
      <div class="board-head">
        <div class="board-title"><span class="mark" style="width:18px;height:18px;border-radius:5px;background:#0F172A;display:inline-block"></span> Dispatch · Thursday, May 14 · 8 loads</div>
        <div class="board-controls"><span>Today</span><span>All drivers</span><span class="mono">$14,250</span></div>
      </div>
      <table class="board-tbl">
        <thead><tr><th>Ref</th><th>Status</th><th>Route</th><th>Pickup</th><th>Driver</th><th class="right">Rate</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td class="mono">L-2026-0142</td><td><span class="pill p-invoiced">Invoiced</span></td><td>Chicago, IL → Indianapolis, IN</td><td>7:30 AM</td><td>Dan Driver</td><td class="right mono">$1,850</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="mono">L-2026-0143</td><td><span class="pill p-delivered">Delivered</span></td><td>Indianapolis, IN → Cleveland, OH</td><td>8:15 AM</td><td>Maria Lopez</td><td class="right mono">$2,100</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="mono">L-2026-0144</td><td><span class="pill p-transit">In transit</span></td><td>St. Louis, MO → Nashville, TN</td><td>9:00 AM</td><td>Carlos Reyes</td><td class="right mono">$1,650</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="mono">L-2026-0145</td><td><span class="pill p-assigned">Assigned</span></td><td>Detroit, MI → Columbus, OH</td><td>10:30 AM</td><td>Marcus Hill</td><td class="right mono">$1,425</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="mono">L-2026-0146</td><td><span class="pill p-assigned">Assigned</span></td><td>Chicago, IL → Milwaukee, WI</td><td>11:00 AM</td><td>Sara Lin</td><td class="right mono">$975</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="mono">L-2026-0147</td><td><span class="pill p-avail">Available</span></td><td>Cleveland, OH → Pittsburgh, PA</td><td>1:00 PM</td><td>—</td><td class="right mono">$1,250</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="mono">L-2026-0148</td><td><span class="pill p-avail">Available</span></td><td>Nashville, TN → Atlanta, GA</td><td>2:00 PM</td><td>—</td><td class="right mono">$1,800</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="mono">L-2026-0149</td><td><span class="pill p-avail">Available</span></td><td>Columbus, OH → Cincinnati, OH</td><td>3:30 PM</td><td>—</td><td class="right mono">$3,200</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="features">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">What FleetFlow does</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Three things, done right, on one screen.</h2>
    <div class="grid-3">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Load board to invoice in one tab</h3>
        <p>Match a load, assign a driver, capture the signed BOL, trigger the invoice — without re-typing anything.</p>
        <span class="benefit"><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M16.7 5.3a1 1 0 0 1 0 1.4l-8 8a1 1 0 0 1-1.4 0l-4-4a1 1 0 0 1 1.4-1.4L8 12.6l7.3-7.3a1 1 0 0 1 1.4 0z"/></svg> Kill 4–6 hrs of admin per truck per week</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Compliance that nags itself</h3>
        <p>HOS, IFTA quarter cutoffs, CDL expirations, DOT medicals — we watch them and ping the right person at the right time.</p>
        <span class="benefit"><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M16.7 5.3a1 1 0 0 1 0 1.4l-8 8a1 1 0 0 1-1.4 0l-4-4a1 1 0 0 1 1.4-1.4L8 12.6l7.3-7.3a1 1 0 0 1 1.4 0z"/></svg> Stop eating a $1,200 violation for a missed date</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Same-day carrier pay</h3>
        <p>Driver hits "delivered," BOL clears, ACH lands the same business day — or next morning if it's after 4pm ET.</p>
        <span class="benefit"><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M16.7 5.3a1 1 0 0 1 0 1.4l-8 8a1 1 0 0 1-1.4 0l-4-4a1 1 0 0 1 1.4-1.4L8 12.6l7.3-7.3a1 1 0 0 1 1.4 0z"/></svg> Get paid 30–45 days faster than NET-30</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="how" style="background:#fff;border-top:1px solid var(--line);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">How it works</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Three steps. No deck. No 6-week onboarding.</h2>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <h3>Setup in 90 minutes</h3>
        <p>Import trucks, drivers, and lanes from a CSV or paste from Sheets. We connect your ELD, factoring company if you use one, and your bank for ACH.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <h3>Dispatch from your phone</h3>
        <p>Drivers get loads, directions, and BOL capture in the app. You see every truck, every load, and every document from one board — at the yard or at the kitchen table.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <h3>Get paid the day you deliver</h3>
        <p>Signed BOL plus rate confirmation triggers the invoice. Brokered loads route through our ACH rails for same-day pay. Direct-shipper loads invoice automatically with your terms.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="pricing">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="price">
      <div>
        <h2>$45 per truck, per month. That's it.</h2>
        <p>No setup fees. No per-driver charges. No contracts. Cancel anytime, export everything to CSV on the way out.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Unlimited users (dispatchers, drivers, accounting)</li>
          <li>ELD integration (Motive, Samsara, Geotab, Garmin)</li>
          <li>IFTA mileage reporting and quarterly export</li>
          <li>Document storage (BOL, POD, rate cons, COI)</li>
          <li>Same-day ACH payouts (standard rates apply)</li>
          <li>Driver mobile app (PWA)</li>
          <li>Support by text and phone</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="founder">★ Founder rate: first 50 fleets lock in <strong>$27/truck for life</strong>. Free first year for design partners.</div>
      </div>
      <div style="text-align:right">
        <div class="num">$45<span style="font-size:24px;color:#94A3B8;font-weight:500">/truck/mo</span></div>
        <div class="per">Billed monthly · ACH or card · USD</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="faq" style="background:#fff;border-top:1px solid var(--line);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)">
  <div class="wrap" style="max-width:820px">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">Common questions</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">The five things every carrier asks first.</h2>

    <details class="q"><summary>Which ELDs and integrations do you support?</summary>
      <p>Motive, Samsara, Geotab, and Garmin eLog today. QuickBooks Online for the books. TriumphPay, OTR Capital, and RTS for factoring. If you're on something else, tell us — we add what design partners need.</p>
    </details>

    <details class="q"><summary>Is there a contract or minimum?</summary>
      <p>No. Month-to-month, cancel from inside the app, no exit calls. You own your data and can export everything to CSV on the way out.</p>
    </details>

    <details class="q"><summary>What about IFTA and factoring?</summary>
      <p>IFTA mileage by jurisdiction is built in — we generate the quarterly report you hand to your accountant or filer. Factoring is optional; we'll plug into your existing factor or pay you direct same-day if you prefer to skip the factoring fee.</p>
    </details>

    <details class="q"><summary>How is my data secured?</summary>
      <p>Encrypted in transit and at rest, SOC 2 Type I in progress, US-based hosting, role-based permissions so your driver doesn't see your margins. We don't sell your load or rate data to anyone, ever.</p>
    </details>

    <details class="q"><summary>What if I grow past 50 trucks?</summary>
      <p>The product scales fine — we have brokers running 80+ carriers on it. Past 50 trucks the per-truck price drops to $35, and you get a dedicated rep. If you need McLeod-grade enterprise features, we'll tell you honestly.</p>
    </details>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="cta">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="final">
      <h2>Try it for 30 days. No card up front.</h2>
      <p>If FleetFlow doesn't save your dispatcher at least 5 hours a week by day 14, we'll get on a call and either fix it or help you move back to Sheets — we'll even export the data clean.</p>
      <div class="cta-row" style="justify-content:center">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#">Start the 30-day trial →</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="#">Book a 20-min call with the founder</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <div class="wrap foot-row">
    <div>© 2026 FleetFlow TMS · Made for small carriers, by people who rode with them.</div>
    <div><a href="#" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:none;margin:0 10px">Terms</a><a href="#" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:none;margin:0 10px">Privacy</a><a href="#" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:none;margin:0 10px">Status</a><a href="#" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:none;margin:0 10px">Changelog</a></div>
  </div>
</footer>

</body></html>
